1) Create User
Method: POST
Endpoint: /users
Body (JSON):
{}
Expected Response: 200 OK

2) Update Level
Method: POST
Endpoint: /users/updateLevel
Body (JSON):
{
  "userId": 1,
  "joinedPopTheBalloonEvent": false
}
Expected Response: 200 OK
Returns updated level, coins, and helium (if event joined).
The "joinedPopTheBalloonEvent" is placeholder, even if it is written as true, if not event joined,
helium will not increase. when the user joins the event, helium will increase.

